column34: In the recent trial between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, we saw and hear her testimony on the stand and everyone who sided with her. The verdict came and the juries declared mister Depp winner and victim of defamation. She should pay him 15 millions dollars for compensatory dammages and JD should pay her 2M$ for mister Waldman's tweet about AH. Tho she was warned many time that she could be called for perjury, she wasnt at the end of the trial. So this petition is for the court to revise the case and make the judgment that she lied under oath, so she (and the others that lied with her) could face some jail time for commiting perjury. They probably will or wont do it cause it was a civil and not a criminal case...put perjury is perjury whatever the context.
